@NODE "FAQ" "Frequently Asked Questions"

 @{FG SHINE}@{U}Frequently Asked Questions@{UU}:@{FG TEXT}

   Q = Question
   A = Answer
   S = Solution

   Q: What does this mean?
      +++ Error 14 in line 254: Requested library not found
      +++ Error 14 in line 245: Requested library not found
      Command returned 10/14: Requested library not found
   A: It can't find one of the libraries it needs.
   S: Copy rexxreqtools.library, tritionrexx.library and rexxtricks.library
      to LIBS: .

   Q: Why doesn't it work from DOpus?
   A: I have some trouble with dopus commands like {f}, it adds "" around
      the filename and I don't know how to remove them in an easy way...
   S: Make the buttons as I have shown in this guide. Click @{"here" LINK "DOpusbuttons"} to
      check how the buttons should look like.
@ENDNODE

